graph TD
    subgraph "Guardrails Regex Detector — RBAC"
        direction TB

        Note["⚠ No RBAC Resources Defined<br/><br/>This component has no ClusterRoles,<br/>RoleBindings, or ServiceAccount<br/>configurations in its repository.<br/><br/>RBAC is expected to be managed by:<br/>• rhods-operator (RHOAI platform)<br/>• FMS Guardrails orchestrator manifests<br/>• Namespace-level policies"]
    end

    subgraph "Authentication"
        direction TB

        Health["/health<br/>GET"]
        API["/api/v1/text/contents<br/>POST"]

        HealthAuth["Auth: None<br/>Unauthenticated"]
        APIAuth["Auth: None<br/>Network isolation only"]

        Health --- HealthAuth
        API --- APIAuth
    end

    subgraph "Security Controls"
        direction TB

        NetworkIsolation["Network-Level Isolation<br/>• ClusterIP service (no external access)<br/>• Pod network policies (external)<br/>• Namespace boundaries"]
        NoTLS["No Application TLS<br/>• Plaintext HTTP only<br/>• Relies on service mesh mTLS<br/>  if deployed with OSSM"]
        NoCrypto["No Crypto Operations<br/>• Pure text processing<br/>• No secrets consumed<br/>• No certificates loaded"]
    end

